  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>Delete</TypeRef> method destroys the console target object.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Important">
      <Paragraph>
        Destroying the target closes any console handle that is still open.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
